{"tid":936714,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"（I/A/PC) 夢幻模擬戰（28）新卡池呢？","createTime":"2018-12-11T03:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T06:50:11.000Z","uid":55835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9183cd940aa36a2ab8930f52241ebc8fd7c7f34c","tid":936714,"uid":55835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T03:45:59.000Z","msg":"[I/A/PC] 夢幻模擬戰(??) - 標題自己諗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nivsWV6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnivsWV6.png&h=53965908&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZX1scuq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZX1scuq.png&h=22d004fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Chym1nK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FChym1nK.png&h=a0dbc157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官網：<a href=\"http://mz.game-beans.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmz.game-beans.com&d=HBUYAvvS2hiLONQlwd7QIP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=5b14f119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://mz.game-beans.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cvOeEZa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcvOeEZa.jpg&h=5fc908a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n殘體注意：陸服有傳之後會有軌跡合作角色<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tieba.baidu.com/p/5964106392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F5964106392&d=HBUYAvvS2hiLONQlwd7QIP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=123aee73\" target=\"_blank\">https://tieba.baidu.com/p/5964106392</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">首抽開局推介:</span><br />\n<br />\n越出越多角色  每個陣營需要既核心角色都唔同<br />\n<br />\n有疑問直接留言問巴打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">新手 FAQ:</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 陣營有乜用?</span><br />\n<br />\nA: 遊戲角色分 8 大陣營：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6V6oXca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6V6oXca.jpg&h=44917994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bs2Lq5w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbs2Lq5w.jpg&h=c0cb3f17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BrTiL5w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBrTiL5w.jpg&h=7d907dbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BCq1JSc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBCq1JSc.jpg&h=3f066e24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EU5AOiS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEU5AOiS.jpg&h=5b95b1ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8e3Sd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8e3Sd.jpg&h=68687362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/20TKGDT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F20TKGDT.jpg&h=fc1f95d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BswWTiH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBswWTiH.jpg&h=4947ff87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n35級後有超絕buff要同陣營先食到(攻擊智力防+20% 魔防+30%)唔同超招再有額外效果<br />\n<br />\n所以建議培養同陣營角色方便食到超絕buff<br />\n<br />\n由於資源有限 <strong>強烈建議集中玩一個陣營</strong><br />\n<br />\n但新手對陣營通常都會理解唔到  <br />\n<br />\n目前比較多人玩係光輝帝國  光輝最平民 無課都組得起  <br />\n<br />\n公主聯盟偏向法師為主   但比較難齊角<br />\n<br />\n黑暗偏向PVP  <br />\n<br />\n真係唔知點揀，一係抽左角再決定<br />\n<br />\n一係上黎問問巴打們<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6KEBB4N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6KEBB4N.png&h=d2126b9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 新手點升Rank好?</span><br />\n<br />\nA: 1體=1經 組隊有折扣   前期建議組隊刷兄貴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 卡關點算?</span><br />\n<br />\nA: 強化裝備 SR照突破升  拆左會退返錢同槌仔比你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 有冇 TG Group?</span><br />\n<br />\nA: 單機 Game 有乜野係度講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 買體幾石？</span><br />\n<br />\nA: 每日40--&gt;60--&gt;100--&gt;150--&gt;200<br />\n<br />\n建議前期可以多買體追LV  等到40後先買少D<br />\n<br />\n睇返自己經濟狀況決定<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 轉職石點用？</span><br />\n<br />\nA: 每一階職第一次開係免費，所以無輪你點升都好 要精通曬2條線要2粒石，已經精通既職業可以用錢互轉，轉2階 5000錢，轉3階30000錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 特權有冇用？買邊隻好</span><br />\n<br />\nA: 廢話論：最好買哂3隻  現實:勇氣--&gt;時鐘--&gt;女神<br />\n<br />\n首先前期體力最重要  時鐘可以幫你唔夠打既時候慳體或者回帶過關<br />\n<br />\n重點8蚊一個月夠哂平  但前期卡關比較容易  可以考慮30-40級後再買<br />\n<br />\n勇氣(女神兄貴獎勵+1) 40級後女神會出光輝秘銀石可以升SSR裝<br />\n<br />\n多一場進度就差好遠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 點課金最抵?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\nA: 現時唔同額嘅首次增值都會有double 石<br />\n<br />\n課晒手機版優惠嘅巴打，請轉開PC版<br />\n<br />\nPC 版同手機版一樣<br />\n<br />\n現時唔同額嘅首次增值都會有double 石<br />\n<br />\nPC 版同手機版係分開計<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPC版mycard增值教學:<br />\n<br />\nNT$1=mycard 1點<br />\n<br />\n入手方法:7-11, OK, 2000fun<br />\n<br />\n1000點=HKD 265<br />\n<br />\n你打開PC版，揀想課石面額<br />\n<br />\n然後會彈去增值網頁<br />\n<br />\n入返張單嘅卡序號同密碼<br />\n<br />\n咁就完成<br />\n<br />\nMycard 增值獎品會起game內信封出現<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 想退款，會唔會被 ban  account ?</span><br />\n<br />\nA: 官方有講過話會打擊惡意退款, 仲整張 email 黎叫退款人入返錢俾佢，唔係告退款人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 附魔初中高級有咩分別？</span><br />\n<br />\nA: 效果一樣  只係刷到好屬性既機率唔同  建議用秘銀石每星期可以換50張中級附魔卷<br />\n<br />\n用中級附魔卷刷就夠   新手可以用4個初級是但附上去拎套裝加成<br />\n<br />\n唔知附邊隻好  就上黎問問巴打們<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裝備評價(只供參考  升錯裝唔負責)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=33596&amp;snA=3365&amp;tnum=10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D33596%26snA%3D3365%26tnum%3D10&d=HBUYAvvS2hiLONQlwd7QIP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=956c0cc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=33596&amp;snA=3365&amp;tnum=10</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://wiki.joyme.com/langrisser/%E5%85%A8SSR%E8%A3%85%E5%A4%87%E6%8C%87%E5%8C%97#.E5.A4.9C.E9.B9.B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwiki.joyme.com%2Flangrisser%2F%25E5%2585%25A8SSR%25E8%25A3%2585%25E5%25A4%2587%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258C%2597%23.E5.A4.9C.E9.B9.B0&d=HBUYAvvS2hiLONQlwd7QIP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=91d00fd8\" target=\"_blank\">http://wiki.joyme.com/langrisser/%E5%85%A8SSR%E8%A3%85%E5%A4%87%E6%8C%87%E5%8C%97#.E5.A4.9C.E9.B9.B0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1001開post :<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跨服好友List：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ffa01dd4cb6724f5f2fd48c3fe45f32f4e7974","tid":936714,"uid":55835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T03:46:29.000Z","msg":"屌，原來我1001左<br />\n<br />\n自隊一打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0f8699bceea735258b3baeff674d1a9b0234d3","tid":936714,"uid":55835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T04:21:52.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4c3ab5d9f6542cd54e7e8ab4de72ba4e00446e","tid":936714,"uid":55835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T12:18:00.